{"tid":1221070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法官謝沈智慧：They (差人) are well paid for it!","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:34:38.000Z","uid":53003,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0dfb7468a81f5e0d702a8a9247e9e46363fb373a","tid":1221070,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170218/large/1487419716_636b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170218%2Flarge%2F1487419716_636b.png&h=cf2d0f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2013年警司貪取食店折扣案 <br />\n2013年，沈智慧審理灣仔分區指揮官的警司黃冠豪，貪取食店折扣一案時，無視中聯辦、警隊一哥曾偉雄等與為被告撰寫的六十多封求情信，更對被告「無功都有勞」的求情理由嗤之以鼻，指「警察唔係免費服務社會㗎！They are well paid for it!」最後重判他入獄一年。 <br />\n<br />\n沈智慧的判詞大快人心，被網民歌頌為「沈青天」、「最美麗法官」。"},{"pid":"6a09389b4ce3fa920531e20744445e4d100e8595","tid":1221070,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"Not anymore.<br />\n<br />\nThey should not be paid for bullying Hong Kong citizens."}]}